2. Mirror the same routing change into the cvl.4 inline clone at `packages/exploration_flutter/test/binding_e2e_integration_test.dart` (lines 82-116, the `_BindingVmServiceFake` class). Replace the `corePrefix`/`pluginPrefix` if/else block with the registry-lookup form from step 1, keeping the class private (`_BindingVmServiceFake`) and the file-local conventions (e.g. the leading-underscore name).

