## Implementation Plan

1. Create `manifest_probe.dart` — `packages/exploration_devtools/lib/src/manifest_probe.dart` (new). Sealed `ManifestProbeResult` with four states + `ManifestProbe` typedef.
   ```dart
   import 'package:exploration_agent/exploration_agent.dart'
       show PluginManifestEntry;

   sealed class ManifestProbeResult { const ManifestProbeResult(); }
   class ManifestProbeLoading extends ManifestProbeResult {
     const ManifestProbeLoading();
   }
   class ManifestProbeLoaded extends ManifestProbeResult {
     const ManifestProbeLoaded(this.plugins);
     final List<PluginManifestEntry> plugins;
   }
   class ManifestProbeBindingMissing extends ManifestProbeResult {
     const ManifestProbeBindingMissing();
   }
   class ManifestProbeFailed extends ManifestProbeResult {
     const ManifestProbeFailed(this.message);
     final String message;
   }
   typedef ManifestProbe =
       Future<List<PluginManifestEntry>> Function(Uri vmServiceUri);
   ```
   Test: `flutter test packages/exploration_devtools/test/manifest_probe_test.dart` (added in step 6) → PASS.
   Commit: `feat(devtools): add ManifestProbeResult sealed type`.

2. Add `defaultManifestProbe` — same file. Uses `VmServiceClient` already exported by `package:exploration_agent`; no new agent surface.
   ```dart
   import 'package:exploration_agent/exploration_agent.dart'
       show VmServiceClient;

   Future<List<PluginManifestEntry>> defaultManifestProbe(Uri uri) async {
     final c = await VmServiceClient.connect(uri);
     try {
       return (await c.handshake()).plugins;
     } finally {
       await c.dispose();
     }
   }
   ```
   Test: covered by step 6 stubs; production path validated by step 7 dogfood.
   Commit: `feat(devtools): add defaultManifestProbe via VmServiceClient`.

3. Extend `ExplorationPanelHost` — `packages/exploration_devtools/lib/src/panel_host.dart`. Add a `ManifestProbe manifestProbe` constructor field defaulting to `defaultManifestProbe`. Add `ValueNotifier<ManifestProbeResult> _manifest` initialized to `ManifestProbeLoading()` and a `_probeGen` counter to drop stale results. Expose `ValueListenable<ManifestProbeResult> get manifest => _manifest`. Call `refreshManifest()` from `initState`. Dispose `_manifest` in `dispose`.
   ```dart
   Future<void> refreshManifest() async {
     final raw = widget.vmServiceUri();
     final gen = ++_probeGen;
     _manifest.value = const ManifestProbeLoading();
     if (raw == null) {
       if (gen == _probeGen && mounted) {
         _manifest.value = const ManifestProbeBindingMissing();
       }
       return;
     }
     try {
       final plugins = await widget.manifestProbe(Uri.parse(raw));
       if (gen != _probeGen || !mounted) return;
       _manifest.value = ManifestProbeLoaded(plugins);
     } on BindingNotInitializedError {
       if (gen != _probeGen || !mounted) return;
       _manifest.value = const ManifestProbeBindingMissing();
     } catch (e) {
       if (gen != _probeGen || !mounted) return;
       _manifest.value = ManifestProbeFailed(e.toString());
     }
   }
   ```
